><!----><!----></section><!----><!----></app-block-wrapper></app-title><!----><ndc-dynamic ngh="0"></ndc-dynamic><app-faq-list _nghost-picflow-c4020821130 ngh="21"><app-block-wrapper _ngcontent-picflow-c4020821130 class="inherit section undefined no-horizontal-padding in-wrapper" ngh="4"><section class="mobile-spacing-bottom- mobile-spacing-top- page spacing-bottom-0 spacing-top-0 standard-spacing small-spacing headless bottomless" style="--max-page-width: 880px; --max-page-width-mobile: 880px;"><!----><div _ngcontent-picflow-c4020821130 class><app-faq-list-item _ngcontent-picflow-c4020821130 _nghost-picflow-c3772357822 class ngh="0"><button _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-xi9bnqrkgg" jsaction="click:;" ngb="d9"><span _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822>What is Picflow?</span><app-svg _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 src="/assets/icons/minus.svg" style="mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg); -webkit-mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg);" ngh="0"></app-svg><app-svg _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 src="/assets/icons/minus.svg" style="mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg); -webkit-mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg);" ngh="0"></app-svg></button><div _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 role="region" class="toggler-body" style="max-height: 0;" id="faq-xi9bnqrkgg"><div _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 class="toggler-body-content standard-text"><div _ngcontent-picflow-c4020821130><p>Picflow is an online proofing and digital asset management platform for creative professionals. It lets you create branded client galleries, collect feedback through favorites, comments and annotations, manage approvals, and securely share and transfer media files — all in one place.</p></div></div></div></app-faq-list-item><app-faq-list-item _ngcontent-picflow-c4020821130 _nghost-picflow-c3772357822 class ngh="0"><button _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-kdq2ng0s8t" jsaction="click:;" ngb="d9"><span _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822>Who is Picflow for?</span><app-svg _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 src="/assets/icons/minus.svg" style="mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg); -webkit-mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg);" ngh="0"></app-svg><app-svg _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 src="/assets/icons/minus.svg" style="mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg); -webkit-mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg);" ngh="0"></app-svg></button><div _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 role="region" class="toggler-body" style="max-height: 0;" id="faq-kdq2ng0s8t"><div _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 class="toggler-body-content standard-text"><div _ngcontent-picflow-c4020821130><p>Picflow is built for photographers, creative agencies, marketing teams, design studios, and any professional who needs to share visual assets and collect client feedback. Whether you're a freelance photographer delivering wedding galleries or a marketing team reviewing campaign assets, Picflow streamlines your workflow.</p></div></div></div></app-faq-list-item><app-faq-list-item _ngcontent-picflow-c4020821130 _nghost-picflow-c3772357822 class ngh="0"><button _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-pb7g2fsjdv" jsaction="click:;" ngb="d9"><span _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822>Is Picflow free to use?</span><app-svg _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 src="/assets/icons/minus.svg" style="mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg); -webkit-mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg);" ngh="0"></app-svg><app-svg _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 src="/assets/icons/minus.svg" style="mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg); -webkit-mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg);" ngh="0"></app-svg></button><div _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 role="region" class="toggler-body" style="max-height: 0;" id="faq-pb7g2fsjdv"><div _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 class="toggler-body-content standard-text"><div _ngcontent-picflow-c4020821130><p>Yes. Picflow offers a free plan with no time limit that includes 2 GB of storage, unlimited galleries, and unlimited collaborators. Paid plans start with a 7-day free trial so you can test the full feature set before committing.</p></div></div></div></app-faq-list-item><app-faq-list-item _ngcontent-picflow-c4020821130 _nghost-picflow-c3772357822 class ngh="0"><button _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-zu8uktvvnq" jsaction="click:;" ngb="d9"><span _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822>What file types does Picflow support?</span><app-svg _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 src="/assets/icons/minus.svg" style="mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg); -webkit-mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg);" ngh="0"></app-svg><app-svg _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 src="/assets/icons/minus.svg" style="mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg); -webkit-mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg);" ngh="0"></app-svg></button><div _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 role="region" class="toggler-body" style="max-height: 0;" id="faq-zu8uktvvnq"><div _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 class="toggler-body-content standard-text"><div _ngcontent-picflow-c4020821130><p>Picflow supports all common image formats (JPEG, PNG, TIFF, WEBP, HEIC), RAW files from major camera brands (CR2, CR3, NEF, ARW, DNG, and more), videos (MP4, MOV up to 4K HDR), and audio files. RAW files are automatically converted to high-quality previews.</p></div></div></div></app-faq-list-item><app-faq-list-item _ngcontent-picflow-c4020821130 _nghost-picflow-c3772357822 class ngh="0"><button _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-vwym5s61qh" jsaction="click:;" ngb="d9"><span _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822>How does the proofing and approval process work?</span><app-svg _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 src="/assets/icons/minus.svg" style="mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg); -webkit-mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg);" ngh="0"></app-svg><app-svg _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 src="/assets/icons/minus.svg" style="mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg); -webkit-mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg);" ngh="0"></app-svg></button><div _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 role="region" class="toggler-body" style="max-height: 0;" id="faq-vwym5s61qh"><div _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 class="toggler-body-content standard-text"><div _ngcontent-picflow-c4020821130><p>You upload your assets, create a gallery, and share a branded review link with your client. They can mark favorites, leave comments with annotations directly on images, apply color labels, and set approval statuses — all without needing an account. You get real-time notifications on all activity.</p></div></div></div></app-faq-list-item><app-faq-list-item _ngcontent-picflow-c4020821130 _nghost-picflow-c3772357822 class ngh="0"><button _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-5zxknjpbf6" jsaction="click:;" ngb="d9"><span _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822>Do clients need an account to review?</span><app-svg _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 src="/assets/icons/minus.svg" style="mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg); -webkit-mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg);" ngh="0"></app-svg><app-svg _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 src="/assets/icons/minus.svg" style="mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg); -webkit-mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg);" ngh="0"></app-svg></button><div _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 role="region" class="toggler-body" style="max-height: 0;" id="faq-5zxknjpbf6"><div _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 class="toggler-body-content standard-text"><div _ngcontent-picflow-c4020821130><p>No. Clients and external reviewers can access galleries, leave feedback, and download files without creating an account. You can have unlimited reviewers on any plan — a license is only needed to create and manage galleries.</p></div></div></div></app-faq-list-item><app-faq-list-item _ngcontent-picflow-c4020821130 _nghost-picflow-c3772357822 class ngh="0"><button _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-o9gdh2882k" jsaction="click:;" ngb="d9"><span _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822>Can I use my own branding?</span><app-svg _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 src="/assets/icons/minus.svg" style="mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg); -webkit-mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg);" ngh="0"></app-svg><app-svg _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 src="/assets/icons/minus.svg" style="mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg); -webkit-mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg);" ngh="0"></app-svg></button><div _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 role="region" class="toggler-body" style="max-height: 0;" id="faq-o9gdh2882k"><div _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 class="toggler-body-content standard-text"><div _ngcontent-picflow-c4020821130><p>Yes. You can upload your logo, set brand colors, connect a custom domain (e.g., gallery.yourbrand.com), and remove the Picflow badge on paid plans. Every gallery link reflects your brand, not ours.</p></div></div></div></app-faq-list-item><app-faq-list-item _ngcontent-picflow-c4020821130 _nghost-picflow-c3772357822 class ngh="0"><button _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-ry6244t009" jsaction="click:;" ngb="d9"><span _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822>Does Picflow integrate with my existing tools?</span><app-svg _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 src="/assets/icons/minus.svg" style="mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg); -webkit-mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg);" ngh="0"></app-svg><app-svg _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 src="/assets/icons/minus.svg" style="mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg); -webkit-mask-image: url(/assets/icons/minus.svg);" ngh="0"></app-svg></button><div _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 role="region" class="toggler-body" style="max-height: 0;" id="faq-ry6244t009"><div _ngcontent-picflow-c3772357822 class="toggler-body-content standard-text"><div _ngcontent-picflow-c4020821130><p>Yes. Picflow integrates with Adobe Lightroom Classic, Capture One, Dropbox, Google Drive, Box, and Zapier. You c